OL,3,CLGBTQ+ asylum seekers in the UK: The
OL,4,Cstruggles of fleeing violence
OL,6,FIt was back in 2019 when Virginia
OL,7,FWairimu says she was forced on her
OL,8,Fjourney to seek asylum.
OL,10,FShe'd been outed as a lesbian in her
OL,11,Fhome country of Kenya and fled,
OL,12,Fseeking sanctuary and safety in the UK.
OL,14,FThe Home Office has since rejected her
OL,15,Fasylum application twice because it
OL,16,Fsays her evidence is inconsistent, and
OL,17,Fthat she hasn't provided enough
OL,18,Fevidence for it to believe her life
OL,19,Fwould be in danger were she to return
OL,20,Fto Kenya.
