OL,3,CLGBTQ+ asylum seekers in the UK: The
OL,4,Cstruggles of fleeing violence
OL,6,FVirginia, 51, told ITV News Central
OL,7,Fshe fled for her safety: "After trying
OL,8,Fto hide for a long time, I got into a
OL,9,Frelationship and we tried to be
OL,10,Fdiscreet, but somehow it became public
OL,11,Fand we were attacked, both me and my
OL,12,Fpartner. Then, after some time, I
OL,13,Fstarted getting threats, and then I
OL,14,Fwas attacked in front of my children."
OL,16,FSoon after, she says she escaped.
