OL,6,FWhen asked about what she'd say to the
OL,7,FHome Office in response to it saying
OL,8,Fshe can live a safe life in Kenya,
OL,9,FVirginia said: "I'll say that's a big
OL,10,Flie. Because I was living a very
OL,11,Fcomfortable life. I would not have
OL,12,Fleft my job, my children, my family
OL,13,Ffor anything.
