OL,3,CLGBTQ+ asylum seekers in the UK: The
OL,4,Cstruggles of fleeing violence
OL,6,FShe continued: "My job was very
OL,7,Finteresting, telling people about
OL,8,FKenya, selling safaris, going to the
OL,9,Fpark. I was actually in a holiday
OL,10,Fmood, and I was being paid. Why would
OL,11,FI come here? To get charity things and
OL,12,Fgo to the food bank? I've never owned
OL,13,Fsecond hand clothes, it was only once
OL,14,FI came to this country...If Kenya was
OL,15,Fsafe, I would be on the next flight
OL,16,Fback home."
