OL,3,CLGBTQ+ asylum seekers in the UK: The
OL,4,Cstruggles of fleeing violence
OL,6,FVirginia says she's struggled with
OL,7,Fwhat she calls a brutal asylum
OL,8,Fapplication process when she first
OL,9,Fcame to the UK, saying she's paid the
OL,10,Fprice for it ever since.
OL,12,FShe told ITV News Central reporter
OL,13,FRaheem Rashid: "When I went for my
OL,14,Ffirst substantial interview, it was a
OL,15,Fvery difficult period. In fact, I
OL,16,Fwould never want to give such a kind
OL,17,Fof an interview again. It was very
OL,18,Fintimidating, very intimate questions,
OL,19,Fand I was very traumatised.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
