OL,6,FShe added: "Most of the answers I was
OL,7,Fnot able to answer correctly, as
OL,8,Fexpected by the interviewer, because
OL,9,Fhe was asking me about things that I
OL,10,Fhad lived for more than 30 years being
OL,11,Ftold was wrong, evil, and satanic. He
OL,12,Fwanted me to tell him everything about
OL,13,Fmy life.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/17
