OL,3,CLGBTQ+ asylum seekers in the UK: The
OL,4,Cstruggles of fleeing violence
OL,6,FIt's for asylum seekers in Birmingham
OL,7,Fwho want to share their stories - both
OL,8,Fgood and bad.
OL,10,FThere, one asylum seeker anonymously
OL,11,Fspoke to ITV News Central, saying the
OL,12,Fwhole application process is
OL,13,Fdehumanising.
OL,15,FHe said: "This system is very
OL,16,Fhorrible, very, very horrible, and you
OL,17,Fdon't know what's going to happen on
OL,18,Fthe next day.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/17
