OL,6,F"After a long journey for the
OL,7,Finterview, maybe 4 hours, one month
OL,8,Flater you receive a post to say, okay,
OL,9,Fyour case is going to be refused.
OL,11,F'It's almost like a game,' Immigration
OL,12,Flawyer Salman Mirza speaks of his
OL,13,Fexperience with the application process
OL,15,FSpeaking of the Home Office's
OL,16,Fapplication process, immigration
OL,17,Flawyer Salman Mirza, said: "I think it
OL,18,Fshould be more about conversation and
OL,19,Fabout getting to the truth rather than
OL,20,Fit being as it is now quite
OL,21,Fadversarial.
