OL,6,F"And it's almost like a game where the
OL,7,FHome Office is trying to catch people
OL,8,Fout. And to me, that's not helpful."
OL,10,FWhen asked about Virginia's case, the
OL,11,FHome Office told ITV News Central its
OL,12,Flongstanding policy is to not comment
OL,13,Fon individual cases, but that it
OL,14,Funderstands individuals may have faced
OL,15,Fdiscrimination or persecution in their
OL,16,Fhome country because of their sexual
OL,17,Forientation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/17
