OL,3,CLGBTQ+ asylum seekers in the UK: The
OL,4,Cstruggles of fleeing violence
OL,6,FBut for refugees like Loraine from
OL,7,FMalawi, even if you do eventually get
OL,8,Fthrough the system, there are new
OL,9,Fchallenges to face.
OL,11,FLoraine said: "It was more than
OL,12,Fdifficult. I claimed asylum in 2015. I
OL,13,Fwas only recognised as a refugee in
OL,14,F2022 and within that period I was made
OL,15,Fhomeless and the pandemic also came
OL,16,Fand I was not on any support."
OL,18,FShe continued: "When I got my status,
OL,19,Feveryone said, 'oh, now she has
OL,20,Fstatus, she's fine now.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/17
