OL,6,FLoraine added: "So all the support you
OL,7,Fhad, it drops, and then you are left
OL,8,Fon your own. Now to navigate the world
OL,9,Fof work where I wasn't working for so
OL,10,Fmany years. And who will employ you in
OL,11,Fthe first place? Because everyone is
OL,12,Flooking for experience. You haven't
OL,13,Fbeen working for many years. Who
OL,14,Fwrites your reference?"
OL,16,FBut while Loraine eventually got
OL,17,Fthrough the system, Virginia still
OL,18,Fhasn't.
