OL,3,CLGBTQ+ asylum seekers in the UK: The
OL,4,Cstruggles of fleeing violence
OL,6,FITV News Central spoke to Virginia
OL,7,Fjust before she went in for one of her
OL,8,Freporting days. She said: "I'm very
OL,9,Fdepressed and quite scared...Honestly,
OL,10,Flast night, I didn't sleep, and I
OL,11,Freally don't sleep because I'm scared
OL,12,Fthat, you know, you won't come out
OL,13,Fbecause we have stories of people
OL,14,Fgoing to report and then they're
OL,15,Fdetained and then they don't tell you
OL,16,Fwhere they're taking you. So every
OL,17,Ftime when I was told that, I was like,
OL,18,Fprobably I'm not going to come back."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/17
