OL,6,FVirginia added: "It's a very
OL,7,Fdepressing situation because I feel
OL,8,Flike I'm very dehumanised, like I'm a
OL,9,Fcriminal. And my only crime is to try
OL,10,Fto look for somewhere safe to live in."
OL,12,FNervously waiting outside Sandford
OL,13,FHouse Reporting Centre was her friend
OL,14,FEmma.
OL,16,FEmma, from Asylum Matters, said: "This
OL,17,Fmental toll is going to be there with
OL,18,Fher, I assume, for the rest of her
OL,19,Flife.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/17
