OL,3,CLGBTQ+ asylum seekers in the UK: The
OL,4,Cstruggles of fleeing violence
OL,6,FShe added: "I just feel personally
OL,7,Fthat she's gone through enough trauma
OL,8,Fback home. She's come to this country
OL,9,Ffor safety and then we're putting her
OL,10,Fthrough this level of trauma."
OL,12,FWhen asked what her eventual goal was
OL,13,Ffrom this whole process, Virginia
OL,14,Fsaid: "I'd like to rebuild my life.
OL,15,FI'd like to get my status. I want to
OL,16,Fhave a meaningful life. I want to have
OL,17,Fa future plan, and probably get love
OL,18,Fand be loved again...It's makes me
OL,19,Ffeel like I'm less of a human being."
